<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">该基地是由江西省职业教育学会艺术专业委员会与井冈山先锋红培基地（省教育厅&ldquo;大思政课&rdquo;实践教学基地）联合共建的实体平台，旨在以井冈山红色文化资源为依托，将红色革命精神与艺术创作、思政教育深度融合。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">会后，艺委会主任刘彦宣布产品设计工作部成立并向工作部成员颁发聘书。江西软件大学当选为产品设计工作部部长单位，江西软件大学VR与艺术学院副院长、江西省职业教育学会艺委会副主任帅茨平担任该工作部部长。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A26%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png?Expires=2063842947&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=FoLJEZlVeRV0ezoD5%2B9VKjt8niI%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A26%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png?Expires=2063842947&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=FoLJEZlVeRV0ezoD5%2B9VKjt8niI%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" /></a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A52%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png?Expires=2063842972&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=9cnGC44NfwcO37SZDGXwmm6KdQA%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A52%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png?Expires=2063842972&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=9cnGC44NfwcO37SZDGXwmm6KdQA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" /></a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A43%3A03%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%879.png?Expires=2063842983&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=kiPMFBd8QrOxk0C8poj7WCy1QOo%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A43%3A03%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%879.png?Expires=2063842983&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=kiPMFBd8QrOxk0C8poj7WCy1QOo%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">最后，艺委会成员与江西软件大学VR与艺术学院师生共同参加了由企业代表上海鸿宇科技总经理雷菁昉主讲的《人工智能为艺术设计赋能》专题讲座，共同感受人工智能对未来艺术专业领域发展的影响。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A43%3A32%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8710.png?Expires=2063843012&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=%2FtzUtbxSuixX2%2F2eIcfi0mokihE%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A43%3A32%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8710.png?Expires=2063843012&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=%2FtzUtbxSuixX2%2F2eIcfi0mokihE%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" /></a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A44%3A00%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8711.png?Expires=2063843040&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=Sjm8tJPgnIyywrzqVSae02L%2FuTU%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A44%3A00%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8711.png?Expires=2063843040&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=Sjm8tJPgnIyywrzqVSae02L%2FuTU%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">&nbsp;本次艺委会重点工作会议是继第四届江西省职业教育学会艺术专业委员会换届工作后召开的一次重要会议，会议明确了艺委会的机构架构，指明了艺委会未来发展方向和目标。未来，江西省职业教育学会艺委会将进一步秉承"服务、交流、合作、发展"的宗旨，不断创新工作思路和方法，努力开创艺委会工作的新局面。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (220, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 5pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">3月31日，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">学校</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">隆重召开本科教学工作合格评估动员大会，全面部署迎评促建工作。学校执行理事长陈方平，校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭及全体在家领导出席会议，全校教职员工参加会议。会议由校务委员徐国荣主持。</span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 5pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 5pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-04-02%2012%3A58%3A0223.jpg?Expires=2058929883&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=4dhrVACuqbaVNrczicHPTHy3Els%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-04-02%2012%3A58%3A0223.jpg?Expires=2058929883&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=4dhrVACuqbaVNrczicHPTHy3Els%3D" width="650" /></a></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 5pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: center; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">高位部署，强化责任</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭作动员讲话。他要求，各责任单位要认真学习评估指标体系，深刻理解内涵，对照指标全面开展自查，列出问题清单，剖析原因，结合学校实际提出改进措施，制订合理的评建工作规划。他强调，</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">一是统一认识，深刻领会职本教学工作合格评估重要意义，适应新常态；二是全面自查，系统梳理职本教学工作合格评估工作任务，明确新方向；三是落实责任，协调形成职本教学工作合格评估工作合力，助推新发展。</span></strong><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #404040; font-size: 18px;">他号召，全校师生以&ldquo;主人翁&rdquo;姿态积极参与，形成&ldquo;人人关心评估、人人参与评估&rdquo;的良好氛围。</span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: center; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">凝心聚力，明确目标</strong></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">校务委员傅志军对《江西软件职业技术大学本科教学工作合格评估建设工作方案》进行了详细解读，包括评估工作的总体要求、目标任务、责任分工及实施步骤。本科教学工作合格评估极其重要，其核心是围绕&ldquo;四个促进&rdquo;&ldquo;三个基本&rdquo; &ldquo;两个突出&rdquo;&ldquo;一个引导&rdquo;展开，大家要遵循&ldquo;以评促建、以评促改、以评促管、评建结合、重在建设&rdquo;20字方针，扎实推动各项工作落实落细。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: center; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">压实责任，立下&ldquo;军令状&rdquo;</strong></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">执行理事长陈方平与校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭，评建专项工作组代表郑重签署了《评建工作责任状》。此举旨在进一步夯实主体责任，清晰界定任务的关键时间节点。各责任单位将以责任状为指引，锚定任务节点，主动作为。各责任人深知责任重大，将带领团队紧锣密鼓推进评建工作，强化协作，确保各环节有序落实，全力迎接评估考验。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">职能部门人事处处长胡梅玲、学院院长代表韩士专教授、教师代表葛伟老师依次发言表态。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (221, '<p>Hello, World!</p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (222, '<p style="margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;">12月6日上午，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开了2024-2025学年第一学期第四次教学工作例会，旨在对11月份教学管理及检查工作进行总结汇报，并布置12月份的具体工作。教务处、质量监测与评估中心负责人，各教学院（部）院长（主任），教学副院长（副主任），教务科长等相关负责人参加了会议，副校长傅志军主持会议并讲话。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20241216/675fcebab760ba23a2900ae9.png" /></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11pt;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;">会议听取了校督导组对于11月份教学活动月督查情况的汇报，总体来看，我校教学活动月举办较为成功，对于提升教师的教学水平起到了一定作用，是一次非常好的教学改革尝试。</span></p>
<p style="margin-right: 0pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10pt; margin-left: 6pt; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 15pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;">教务处处长李嵩对11月份工作进行了总结，并对下一阶段的本、专科专业备案工作、新增专业申报工、学士学位授权专业申报、期末考试安排、岗位实习、毕业设计（论文）等重点工作做了布置安排。教务处副处长王金林对期中教学检查情况进行了通报，结合发现的问题和师生建议反馈，对教学资料、试卷阅卷、教案编写、实验（训）报告、档案室建设等方面做了进一步的规范。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;">会上，副校长傅志军对各教学院（部）在教学活动月付出的努力表示了认可，总结此次教学活动月内容丰富、效果良好，今后要把教学活动月作为教学工作中的基本环节加以坚持。同时强调12月份工作要规范、有序地进行谋划。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;">一是期末考试工作要规范。从命题、制卷、考试、阅卷到成绩评定与录入等，每一个环节都要严格按照既定流程执行，确保考试的公平、公正和有效性。二是涉及本、专科专业申报方面的4项工作要按规定按时保质申报和提交。三是有序推进2025届毕业生岗位实习工作。关心关爱学生，关注学生实习安全，在做好岗位实习工作的同时，兼顾好毕业设计（论文）。四是有条不紊地组织好全国大学英语四、六级考试。五是做好2025版人才培养方案，教务处与公共课教学部要加强联系，各学院要提前捋清本专业的专业基础课、专业核心课、专业选修课并形成目录。六是谋划好本科专业发展规划，拓宽思路，明确好专业发展方向和特色。七是完成好课程建设工作，不断更新和优化课程内容和教学方法，以适应学科发展和学生需求的变化。八是做好2024年总结及2025年工作计划，高度重视，站位要高，对照本科教学合格评估指标，谋划好明年的工作。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10pt; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (223, '<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">1月3日，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开了2024-2025学年第一学期第五次教学工作例会。教务处、质量监测与评估中心负责人，各教学院（部）院长（主任）、教学副院长（副主任）、教务科长等相关负责人参加了会议。副校长傅志军主持会议并讲话。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">会议伊始，校督导组组长黄承烈对12月份的教学督查情况进行了通报。总体来看，本月教学秩序整体平稳，延续了11月教学活动月的积极成果。智能科技学院副院长蒋淦华和软件工程学院副院长李俊传达了北京职业教育项目课程建设研讨会的会议精神。他们围绕职业本科的内涵、&ldquo;五金&rdquo;体系建设、课程设置、专业设置以及人才培养方案的制定等多个层面进行了深入的分享与交流。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20250228/67c12bc0b760ba23a2900af3." /></span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">教务处对近期的工作进行了回顾与安排，强调要抓好期末考试考风考纪，认真完成收尾工作，通报了毕业论文（设计）及岗位实习工作情况，对2024-2025学年第二学期教材征订工作提出了要求，并下发校级毕业设计（论文）抽检管理办法征求意见稿，征集各学院反馈意见。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">会上，傅校长重点强调了几项工作：一是要扎实做好期末考试工作，除了确保考试过程的公平公正，还需细致做好成绩评阅、登分，试卷分析等工作，以便精准反馈教学效果，指导后续教学改进。二是加强本科合格评估材料学习，深入学习理解评估标准，按合格评估指标规范开展各项教学与管理工作。三是高度重视2025届毕业论文（设计）和岗位实习工作，加强过程管理，确保质量达标。四是2025版人才培养方案制定，调整课程设置，强化实践教学，合理规划教学进度、创新课程考核形式，打造特色鲜明的人才培养方案，促进学生全面发展。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (224, '<p style="text-indent: 30pt; line-height: 26pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">近日，江西省高等教育学会举办的2024年度第一届&ldquo;格子达杯&rdquo;优秀本科毕业论文评奖活动结果公布，我校共获得优秀论文指导奖&ldquo;优秀奖&rdquo;3项，优秀论文奖&ldquo;优秀奖&rdquo;3项。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 26pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20250228/67c12a77b760ba23a2900af2.png" /></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 26pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">此次&ldquo;格子达杯&rdquo;优秀本科毕业论文评奖活动，旨在表彰在学术研究、创新思维和实践能力方面表现突出的本科毕业生。我校高度重视本科毕业论文（设计）工作，为加强我校毕业论文（设计）工作的规范管理，进一步提高毕业论文（设计）质量，制发了《江西软件职业技术大学本科毕业论文（设计）指导手册》等文件，为毕业论文（设计）工作提供了制度与组织保障。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 26pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">在此，特向获奖学生及指导教师表示热烈的祝贺！希望全体同学以获奖同学为榜样，勤奋学习、勇于创新，在今后的学术研究和学习实践中取得更优异的成绩。同时，也希望全体教师继续发扬敬业精神，不断提升教学质量和科研水平，为培养更多具有创新能力和实践能力的高素质人才贡献力量。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (225, '<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp; <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 24px;">为扎实推进我校毕业班学生</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px;">岗位实习工作，切实解决工作中遇到的问题，10月31日，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开了2025年毕业班学生岗位实习工作推进会。执行校长范红铭、教务处、校企合作办负责人，各学院院长及教学副院长参加了会议，副校长傅志军主持会议并讲话。</span></p>
<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20241126/67453f83b760ba23a2900ae4.png" /></span></p>
<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px;">&nbsp; 会上各学院对于本学院集中实习安排现状、集中实习公司数量、提供的岗位数（是否充足）、是否做了集中实习宣讲、是否做了对应的集中实习计划、各计划是否配套了指导教师跟踪、目前集中实习安排工作问题及难点、学生实习意愿等方面进行了汇报，分享了各自在实习工作中的亮点和成效，提出了当前实习工作中存在的共性和个性问题。</span></p>
<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px;">&nbsp; 在听取了各学院的汇报和讨论后，执行校长范红铭对2025届学生岗位实习管理工作提出三点要求：一是提高思想认识，强化责任担当。学院要进一步提高对岗位实习工作的重视程度，对标对表的落实本科合格评估指标体系。二是理清头绪，形成合力，动实习就���一体化。各教学单位要准确把握专业定位，细化学生岗位实习的分工安排，加强交流协作，借力借智，共同克服困难，推进各项工作内容落实落细。三是就业工作要潜移默化，贯穿于实习的全过程。实习和就业工作的宣传要潜移默化贯穿于各学习阶段，深化学生对于实习就业的认识，并根据学生的专业特点和实习需求适当调整人才培养方案，采取分段式实习，通过逐步深入的方式，努力高质量完成2025届学生岗位实习管理工作。</span></p>
<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 24px;">&nbsp; 副校长傅志军在会上强调了开展集中实习的重要性，一是基于江西省职业学校学生实习管理平台填报要求，二是本科合格评估的要求，三是提高学生就业率的现实考虑。各教学单位要转变观念，落实上级要求，加强对学生的管理，将实习管理工作做细做实；加强与企业的合作与交流，不断优化实习资源配置，实习基地要重点以南昌周围为主，便于评估专家实地考核；完善实习成果的考核与评估体系，客观公正地评价学生的实习表现。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (226, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">8月29日下午，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开了2024-2025学年第一学期第一次教学工作例会。党委副书记、执行校长范红铭出席会议并讲话，副校长傅志军主持会议。教务处、学工处、质评中心、实验实训中心、校企合作办等职能部门负责人，各教学院（部）院长（主任）、教学副院长（副主任）、教务科长及教务处人员等参加了会议。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-03%2012%3A18%3A04image.png?Expires=2040697085&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=wZjknYf1n6aVWmnNBsEwWRmBhZ0%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-03%2012%3A18%3A04image.png?Expires=2040697085&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=wZjknYf1n6aVWmnNBsEwWRmBhZ0%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">执行校长范红铭强调，教学质量是学校的生命线，新学期要继续坚持问题、目标导向，注重工作细节，扎实做好本学期的教学与管理工作。一是做好本学期教学工作安排，提高教学管理的质量与水平。认真负责地做好学期初各项教学准备、教学资源保障等工作，在工作中要多思考，创新工作思路，提升工作实效性，注重教学成果转化，形成教学合力，高效有序地开展教学工作。二是加强教师队伍建设，提升教学水平和课堂质量。全体教师要树立质量意识，提升教学水平和专业素养，教学有方法，课堂有温度，不断帮助青年教师成长，着力打造优质高效队伍。三是做好实习实训工作，强化实践教学。高度重视实习实训工作，加强与行业企业的合作，继续建立稳定的校外实习基地，强化实习实训过程管理，为学生提供真实的工作环境和实践机会。四是聚焦本科教学合格评估指标体系，提升教育教学质量。各学院（部）要加强各项工作的统筹安排，有针对性地开展教学工作，优化教育教学内容，持续改进和提升教育教学质量。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">副校长傅志军明确提出，新学期的教学与管理工作要以平稳、有序、规范作为基本要求和遵循，紧紧围绕本科教学合格评估指标体系开展各项工作；管理干部要加强学习，不断优化管理流程、改进工作方法、提升工作效率，扎实推进各项工作的落实；各教学院（部）要确保期初教学工作和活动有序进行；重点做好2025届毕业生论文（设计）、岗位实习、本科专业申报以及人才培养方案修订等工作。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">教务处处长李嵩布置了新学期期初教学重点工作，就人才培养工作状态数据采集与管理平台填报工作、期初教学检查工作、2025届毕业班学生岗位实习、毕业论文（设计）抽检等工作作了详细工作要求。质量监测与评估中心督导夏璇全面回顾上一学年的教学督导，并对本学期督导工作进行了部署。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (227, '<p>Hello, World!</p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (228, '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本学年学校共设置有20个本科专业，22个专科专业。本学年，本科新增人工智能工程技术、金融科技应用、大数据与审计、影视编导、物联网工程技术专业，专科现代通信技术专业停招。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a title="附件1：江西软件职业技术大学设置专业一览表(2023-2024学年)" href="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20241111/6731791eb760ba23a2900adf.xlsx">附件1：江西软件职业技术大学设置专业一览表(2023-2024学年)</a></p>
<p><a title="附件2：江西软件职业技术大学停招专业一览表（2023-2024学年）" href="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20241111/67317943b760ba23a2900ae0.xlsx">附件2：江西软件职业技术大学停招专业一览表（2023-2024学年）</a></p>
<p><a title="附件3：江西软件职业技术大学新增专业一览表（2023-2024学年）" href="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20241111/67317961b760ba23a2900ae1.xlsx">附件3：江西软件职业技术大学新增专业一览表（2023-2024学年）</a></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (229, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">4月30日，第十六届蓝桥杯全国软件和信息技术专业人才大赛江西赛区获奖名单公布，我校学生凭借扎实的专业功底与卓越的创新能力，斩获省级一等奖15项，省级二等奖51项，省级三等奖98项，共计164个奖项，获奖率达40%，其中获省级一等奖的同学直接晋级全国赛。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-15%2015%3A14%3A13image.png?Expires=2062653253&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=DNQy7wk4q3SYP7UtW9ObxYhD%2BAY%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-15%2015%3A14%3A13image.png?Expires=2062653253&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=DNQy7wk4q3SYP7UtW9ObxYhD%2BAY%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">蓝桥杯大赛由工业和信息化部人才交流中心主办，国信蓝桥教育科技股份有限公司承办的一项面向全国高校大学生的竞赛，连续五年入选中国高等教育学会 &ldquo;全国普通高校学科竞赛排行榜&rdquo;。大赛紧密围绕当前社会急需的信息技术专业重点领域，着力培养高校大学生的专业IT技能和创新实践能力，是高等教育教学改革和创新人才培养的重要竞赛项目，是以赛促学、以赛促教的大学生科技创新的重要平台。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">本次优异成绩的取得，展现了我校学生优秀的专业素养、心理素质、拼搏精神和创新能力。通过此次赛事，我校师生将认真总结参赛经验，继续抓好以赛促学、以赛促教、以赛促改，进一步完善人才培养模式。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (230, '<p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">为推动我校教学与管理工作高质量发展，5月6日下午，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开了2023-2024学年第二学期第三次教学工作例会。执行校长范红铭，教务处、科技处、人事处、学工处、质评中心、财务处、信息处、实验实训中心、校企合作办、图书馆等主要负责人，各教学院（部）院长（主任）、教学副院长（副主任）、教务科长及教务处人员等参加了会议。傅志军副校长主持会议并讲话。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt;"><br></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: center;"> <img src="/data/upload/editor/1750834701890.jpg" alt="1750834701890.jpg" data-href="/data/upload/editor/1750834701890.jpg" style="width: 492.05px;height: 369.02px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">教务处处长李嵩就4月份的工作进行了总结汇报，并对5月份各项教学工作进行了布置安排。图书馆负责人刘慎河就省文明办、省教育厅举办的第八届“书香伴成长”读书活动的具体安排进行了布置。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">执行校长范红铭在会上强调，要将教学与管理工作摆在学校高质量发展的突出位置，明确好教学基本定位。一是对标本科教学工作合格评估标准的要求，严格规范管理。全面了解评估要求，教学与管理工作要紧紧围绕标准要求展开，不断加强师资队伍建设，提升教师教学水平，鼓励教师多参加含金量高的赛事，争取重点突破。完善教学资源配置，加强教学基础设施建设，规范教学管理，加强质量保障体系建设。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">二是狠抓内涵建设，注重质量提升。在专业建设方面，各学院要提前布局谋划，以市场需求为导向，结合学科发展趋势，不断优化专业结构，做好新专业的申报和建设工作。课程建设是提升教学质量的关键环节，要不断加强课程建设，完善课程体系，更新教学内容和教学方法。积极与企业开展合作，共同建设实践教学基地，为学生提供更多的实践机会。还要加强与企业的沟通和交流，了解企业的需求和反馈，为教学改革提供依据和方向，提高人才竞争力。重视校园文化建设，贯彻落实好“十一工程”。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">三是加强教学工作沟通协调。职能部门应主动与二级学院保持密切联系，了解他们的需求和困难，及时提供帮助和支持。同时，二级学院也应积极参与学校的政策讨论和规划制定，为学校的发展出谋划策；学院与学院间要加强交流互鉴，在教学资源、科研项目等方面进行合作，分享先进经验，共同提升学校的整体实力；教师与学生要形成良性互动，教师应倾听学生的想法和意见，尊重他们的个性和差异，建立良好的师生关系。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">傅校长强调，教学与管理工作要讲规范、重质量、重创新。一是重视实验实训，优化课程成绩评定方式，加大实验实训成绩占比。二是认真落实好期中教学检查，做好基础性工作，形成规范化常态化。三是根据社会需求和学科发展趋势，及时修订人才培养方案。在修订过程中，注重培养学生的实践能力和创新思维，增加实验实训环节的比重，还要注重培养学生的综合素质和人文素养，加强通识教育和选修课程的设置。四是做好毕业论文（设计）工作，全过程严格把关，充分运用好考研成功资源，积极开展考研经验分享活动。五是高度重视教学成果奖，要提高站位，进行宏观设计，在总结过去挖掘有用素材的基础上，进行理论升华，下功夫打磨实力。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (231, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: black;">2025年2月11日，学校召开2024年度民办高校年检工作会议。全体校领导、中层以上干部参加会议。党委副书记、执行校长范红铭主持会议。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-11%2017%3A32%3A55%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2054626375&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=e%2BM9kWdxxz71Lma0L78kz0Or2uw%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-11%2017%3A32%3A55%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2054626375&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=e%2BM9kWdxxz71Lma0L78kz0Or2uw%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" /></a></span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">会上，执行校长范红铭强调，民办高校年检工作是关乎学校生存发展的全局性工作，既是对办学质量的全面考核，也是推动内涵建设的重要契机。年检结果将直接影响招生计划、财政资金分配和评优资格，全校必须站在战略高度统一认识，以问题为导向系统梳理短板，通过查漏补缺强化内部管理、规范依法治校，为学校可持续发展奠定基础。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">为此，他提出三方面核心要求：一是提高政治站位，校领导班子需统筹全局、压实责任，确保理事会与党委会目标落地；各部门须深入学习民办教育法规政策，严格对照《2024年度民办高校年检工作实施方案》及指标体系开展自查自评，精准准备数据和佐证材料。二是聚焦精准发力，主动对接省教育厅评价处室掌握考核动态，深入研读指标内涵与释义，确保理解&ldquo;准、精、全&rdquo;；专家现场核查环节要突出&ldquo;细、优、实&rdquo;，通过任务分工责任制确保每项指标专人跟进、材料完备。三是强化组织保障，严明纪律要求全校上下服从指挥、协同攻坚，杜绝推诿扯皮，对履职不力者严肃问责，以高标准凝聚合力完成迎检任务。</span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">他总结指出，年检既是挑战更是机遇，需将迎检准备与日常管理深度融合，通过规范化、系统化整改推动办学水平全面提升。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: black;">此次会议的召开，不仅为我校2024年度民办高校年检工作指明了方向，更为学校的健康发展注入了新的动力。全校师生将以此为契机，继续努力，共同书写学校发展的新篇章。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (232, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">5月24日，2024-2025年华为ICT大赛2024-2025全球总决赛闭幕式暨颁奖典礼在深圳举行，我校网络工程学院代表队从全球21万余名参赛者中脱颖而出，斩获<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">实践赛网络赛道全球三等奖。</strong></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</strong></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: left; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;" align="center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-30%2010%3A14%3A55%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8712.png?Expires=2063931295&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=WnqDs3RShTWuGBXE0qBAaL04XFk%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-30%2010%3A14%3A55%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8712.png?Expires=2063931295&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=WnqDs3RShTWuGBXE0qBAaL04XFk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" /></a>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">此次获奖不仅是学校深化产教融合的重要里程碑，更是&ldquo;岗课赛证&rdquo;融通育人体系的生动实践。作为江西省首批开展华为ICT学院建设的高校，我校通过与华为共建&ldquo;双师型&rdquo;教学团队、联合开发行业认证课程，将企业真实项目融入专业教学，构建起&ldquo;岗位需求-课程体系-技能竞赛-职业认证&rdquo;四位一体的人才培养闭环。其中，网络工程学院超80%专业核心课程实现教学标准与行业标准、教学内容与岗位需求、教学过程与生产流程对接。将ICT行业最新技术标准转化为教学资源库，近三年已培养出数十名获得HCIE认证的尖端人才。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">该学院将华为认证知识点转化为教学案例，通过&ldquo;项目驱动、实境训练&rdquo;的教学模式，使学生在备赛过程中同步完成企业级项目实践，实现&ldquo;毕业即上岗，上岗即骨干&rdquo;的人才培养目标。近三年，毕业生在华为HCIE认证通过率、华为生态企业录用率等关键指标上领跑江西省同类院校。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">学校��持续深化产教融合、赛教融合改革，通过&ldquo;产业引领、标准对接、实战育人&rdquo;的创新模式，提升学校服务区域现代化产业体系建设和经济社会发展贡献能力和贡献率，培养更多具有国际视野的&ldquo;数智工匠&rdquo;。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #23527c; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; outline-width: 0px; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-30%2010%3A15%3A15%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8713.png?Expires=2063931316&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=o0Yq1%2FELDNyH75CmBYuUcztxPnc%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-30%2010%3A15%3A15%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8713.png?Expires=2063931316&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=o0Yq1%2FELDNyH75CmBYuUcztxPnc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="866" /></a></span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (233, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">近日，为积极响应教育部等九个部门关于开展全国推广普通话宣传周活动的号召，并庆祝教师节、中秋节和国庆节等重要节庆日，我校成功举办了一场别开生面的校园推普海报设计大赛。经评选，此次大赛产生了一等奖1名、二等奖2名、三等奖3名。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-23%2010%3A40%3A16image.png?Expires=2042419216&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=MhFxvj2tJ91rydzWQ8dlepqMn%2BU%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-23%2010%3A40%3A16image.png?Expires=2042419216&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=MhFxvj2tJ91rydzWQ8dlepqMn%2BU%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">本次海报设计大赛以&ldquo;加大推普力度，筑牢强国语言基石&rdquo;为主题，通过学生们的创意作品，充分展示了普通话的独特魅力。活动由教务处负责，VR与艺术学院承办，面向全校学生公开征集作品。学生们积极响应，巧妙地将教师节、中秋节和国庆节等节日元素融入海报设计中，创作出一幅幅富有创意和视觉冲击力的海报。这些优秀作品在校内学术报告厅进行展示，吸引了学生广泛关注。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">此次活动不仅为学生提供了一个展示才华和创意的平台，加深了他们对传统节日的理解和认识，还有效提升了他们的普通话水平和语言文字规范意识。同时，它也在全校范围内营造了浓厚的推广普通话的氛围和文化氛围。未来，我校将继续举办此类活动，进一步推动语言文字工作的深入开展，为铸牢中华民族共同体意识、传承和弘扬中华优秀语言文化奠定坚实的基础。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (234, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">3月28日，我校在A1-102会议室组织召开了2024-2025学年第二学期第三次教学工作例会，教务处、质量监测与评估中心负责人及部门相关人员，各教学院（部）院长（主任），教学副院长（副主任），教务科长等相关负责人参加会议。副校长傅志军主持会议并讲话。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-04-14%2019%3A56%3A50%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2059991811&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=6JxqK0ZHGIeLB2vxVL7iO%2BdGfgs%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 422px;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-04-14%2019%3A56%3A50%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2059991811&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=6JxqK0ZHGIeLB2vxVL7iO%2BdGfgs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="422" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">会议通报了3月份教学督查与实验（训）专项检查情况。从整体来看，教学运行秩序良好，但部分环节仍需改进，对于存在的共性问题要予以重视。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">会议对2025届毕业班学生毕业设计（论文）答辩工作和岗位实习工作提出了要求，并对即将启动的期中教学检查以及近期技能竞赛工作进行了安排，传达了江西省教育厅全省高校招生培养就业联动工作视频会精神，强调了要进一步推进招生计划、人才培养和就业联动机制，提升人才培养质量和服务经济社会发展能力，全面促进毕业生高质量充分就业等。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">副校长傅志军对近期工作重点提出了三点意见：一是要围绕职业教育的属性，解放思想，转变观念。深化校企合作与产教融合，确保专业设置对接国家战略，人才培养规格对接岗位要求，教学内容对接先进工艺、先进技术，教学过程对接企业生产过程，实现&ldquo;理论教学案例化、实践教学项目化、毕业设计实干化&rdquo;。二是要加强学习、担当实干，要认真学习职业教育本质，理解并应用于管理当中，加强基层教学单位和教师的指导，提高教师的能力和水平。三是具体工作布置，包括落实好&ldquo;拓尔思&rdquo;实训项目、认真打磨教学课件、实验（训）指导书编制规范和校外实习基地检查等工作。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (235, '<p class="15" style="text-indent: 30.0000pt; punctuation-trim: leading; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 25.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15.0000pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">为弘扬工匠精神，充分发挥职业技能竞赛在培养学生专业实践能力的作用，提升技术技能人才培养质量，我校于</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">2024年4月至5月组织开展了第十届职业技能大比武，经审核，本届职业技能大比武共363名学生获奖，其中罗永康等68名同学获一等奖，郭文锋等116名同学获二等奖，张思怡等179名同学获三等奖，邹林薏等37名老师获优秀指导老师奖。</span></span></p>
<p class="15" style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 25pt; margin: 0pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15.0000pt; background: #ffffff;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20241226/676cd1cab760ba23a2900aeb.png" /><br /></span></p>
<p class="15" style="text-indent: 30.0000pt; punctuation-trim: leading; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 25.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15.0000pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">本次职业技能大比武参照了江西省职业院校职业技能大赛和江西省大学生科技创新与技能大赛的要求，体现了专业的核心技术技能，展示了���生的综合职业技能。大赛</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15.0000pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">设区块链应用操作竞赛、大数据技术与应用技能竞赛、程序设计竞赛、虚拟现实</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">(VR)交互开发技能竞赛等27个技能竞赛，</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15.0000pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">比赛项目丰富，专业性强。</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15.0000pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">希望同学们再接再厉，在各类竞赛中展示江软学子</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;学好软件，报效祖国&rdquo;和&ldquo;学技能、勇争先&rdquo;的精神风貌。</span></span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (236, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 21.6px; color: black;">2月17日，我校迎来2025年春季学期开学首日。校党委书记、督导专员饶勇，党委副书记、执行校长范红铭带领全校各级领导干部共计71人深入教学一线，与师生共同开启新学期课堂教学序幕，覆盖软件工程学院等9个二级学院、 43个本专科专业、64个教学班级，通过&ldquo;零距离&rdquo;观察课堂教学，为新学期教育教学工作开好局、起好步。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 21.6px; color: black;">按照学校&ldquo;春季开学安全教育周&rdquo;统一部署，教师们首先开展消防安全主题教育，通过观看警示教育片、师生共话消防安全重要性，将安全意识和责任深植学生心中。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 21.6px; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-18%2018%3A31%3A45%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2055234705&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=R3LV1FYS4OESli9hz4JWzJMaPb0%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-18%2018%3A31%3A45%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2055234705&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=R3LV1FYS4OESli9hz4JWzJMaPb0%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 21.6px; color: black;">消防安全教育结束后，教师们根据教学计划，有序开展专业课程和基础课程的教学活动，在简要介绍课程目标、学习要求及考核方式后，正式开启新学期第一讲。学生们以饱满的精神状态投入学习，课堂上专注聆听、踊跃发问。各级领导重点关注&ldquo;师生双主体&rdquo;互动成效，对教师良好的职业素养和精准对接职业能力需求的教学设计，以及学生展现出的积极向上的求知欲望和主动学习的态度给予肯定。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 21.6px; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-18%2018%3A32%3A08%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2055234729&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=FkJaLUnoMqD7IGixYbKJnogP%2BWw%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-18%2018%3A32%3A08%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2055234729&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=FkJaLUnoMqD7IGixYbKJnogP%2BWw%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-18%2018%3A32%3A27%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2055234748&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=Ifb1oswOdhCHOqbXNkCI1lnsH%2Bs%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-02-18%2018%3A32%3A27%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2055234748&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=Ifb1oswOdhCHOqbXNkCI1lnsH%2Bs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" /></a></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 21.6px; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">新学期伊始的教学听课活动，既是对寒假教学备课成效的集中检阅，更是向&ldquo;课堂革命&rdquo;发出的冲锋号角。学校将进一步强化&ldquo;以学生发展为中心&rdquo;的理念，持续完善教育教学评价与反馈机制，推动教学从&ldquo;知识传授&rdquo;向&ldquo;能力塑造&rdquo;转型，不断提升人才培养质量。</span></span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (237, '<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑;">近日，第五届江西省高校教师教学创新大赛获奖名单公布。我校新媒体学院杨婧教师团队主讲的《融合新闻作品创作》获课程思政中级及以下组三等奖，VR与艺术学院李书烨教师团队主讲的《创新设计 I》获新文科副高组三等奖。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"> <img src="/data/upload/editor/1750836023718.png" alt="1750836023718.png" data-href="/data/upload/editor/1750836023718.png" style=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/editor/1750836032393.png" alt="1750836032393.png" data-href="/data/upload/editor/1750836032393.png" style="width: 677.00px;height: 127.69px;"></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">本届大赛由江西省教育厅指导、江西省高等教育学会主办，以“推动教学创新，培养一流人才”为主题，包括基础课程、新工科、新文科、新农科、新医科、课程思政和产教融合7个赛道，汇聚了全省高校众多优秀教师同台竞技。经校赛、省赛两轮严格评审，最终评选出一等奖40项、二等奖85项、三等奖90项，优秀组织奖16项。作为教育部“三评一竞赛”权威赛事之一，其成绩已纳入江西省高等教育质量评估体系，成为衡量高校教学改革成效的重要内容。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">近年来，我校高度重视教学创新与教师队伍建设，积极鼓励教师开展教学改革与实践，为教师搭建各类教学能力提升平台，通过“以赛促教、以赛促改、以赛促建”的方式，鼓励教师积极投身教学创新，有力推动人才培养的高质量发展。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (238, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">8月28日上午，我校在行政楼一楼会议室通过线上方式与圣何塞大学成功召开了&ldquo;创新思维与国际教育融合&rdquo;专题研讨会，此次会议邀请了国内外教育专家、学者参加。我校校长庄力可博士、USJ创校校长Claude Wang博士、美国教育专家Head of School联合总校校长Olaf Jorgenson博士以及USJ特聘教授艾欣博士，共同探讨在全球化背景下，如何通过创新思维推动国际教育的深入发展，培养具有国际竞争力的复合型人才。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-01%2010%3A09%3A3941807ac93c7014c3d5cc51a37ee05a48.png?Expires=2040516580&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=UANYuDocDlfUep8JVnyiiJ8XKIs%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-01%2010%3A09%3A3941807ac93c7014c3d5cc51a37ee05a48.png?Expires=2040516580&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=UANYuDocDlfUep8JVnyiiJ8XKIs%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">会议上，党委副书记、执行校长范红铭主持会议并致欢迎辞，他表示，在全球化日益加深的今天，高校作为知识传播与创新的重要基地，必须积极拥抱变化，将创新思维融入国际教育的每一个环节，以应对未来社会的挑战，并希望本次研讨会能够成为大家交流思想、分享智慧、共谋发展的平台，���发出更多推动教育创新发展的灵感与火花。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">随后，Claude Wang博士、庄力可博士、Olaf Jorgenson博士发表了精彩的主旨演讲，他们结合自身经验和研究成果，强调了面对全球化的挑战与机遇，创新思维在国际教育中的应用和可行性，在&ldquo;创新思维+&rdquo;的引领下，深入培养学生的批判性思维、创新能力和社会责任感，为他们未来的职业发展和社会贡献奠定坚实的基础，学习借助先进科技手段，如人工智能、虚拟现实等，实现教学内容的个性化、教学方法的创新化以及学习方式的灵活化。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-01%2010%3A10%3A246fbd21e17eb55fe6c07fb2191c7b6777.jpg?Expires=2040516624&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=KNM0yPBnqBHgEHibfw36zD61pcw%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-09-01%2010%3A10%3A246fbd21e17eb55fe6c07fb2191c7b6777.jpg?Expires=2040516624&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=KNM0yPBnqBHgEHibfw36zD61pcw%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">USJ特聘教授艾欣博士是一位&ldquo;创新设计思维&rdquo;的先行者，从事创新设计思维培训多年，拥有丰富的创新教育经验，曾为国内外公司、机构、大学等9000多人提供创新培训和顾问服务。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">艾欣博士围绕&ldquo;Design Thinking+ for Future Education&rdquo;主题深入剖析&ldquo;设计思维+&rdquo;的内涵与实践路径。她通过生动的案例，展示了创新设计思维在各行业中的应用与探索，并从&ldquo;什么是设计思维&rdquo;&ldquo;怎么学习设计思维&rdquo;两个方面全面地诠释了这一理念的多样性和普遍性，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">同时提出设计思维的学习规则即三个原则（空杯心态、延迟评判、为错误而欢呼）和一个基本点（保持快乐）</strong>，并设置分组讨论环节，让与会者更加深入地体会到设计思维的趣味性和可操作性。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;">在互动问答环节，与会者根据各自的研究领域和兴趣点，积极向演讲嘉宾提问，共同探讨教育创新中的难点和热点问题。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: black;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">此次研讨会让大家受益匪浅，不仅加深了对创新思维与国际教育融合的理解和认识，也为未来的教育创新实践提供了宝贵的思路和方向</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold;">。</strong>同时，也期待在未来的日子里能够继续加强交流与合作，以&ldquo;创新思维+&rdquo;为引领，共同推动国际教育的繁荣与发展，为培养更多具有全球视野、创新精神和实践能力的人才贡献智慧和力量。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (239, '<p style="text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 22pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">2024年9月2日，江西省职业院校技能大赛执委会公布 2024 年江西省职业院校技能大赛协办单位及承办院校名单。经专家组评审并报大赛组委会审定���确定了2024年拟定常规赛项 153 项（高职组 99 项，中职组 54 项），特色赛项 56 项（高职组 29 项，中职组 27 项）。其中，我校将承办高职组的电子与信息大类的&ldquo;网络舆情监测与分析&rdquo;以及&ldquo;Web 应用软件开发&rdquo;赛项等2项赛事。</span></span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 22pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5000pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5000pt;"> <img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20240910/66dfef6cb760ba236ed6d346.png" /><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://jwc.jxuspt.edu.cn/resource_znkj/20240910/66dfef6cb760ba236ed6d347.png" /></span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 22pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">江</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">西省职业院校技能大赛是我省职业教育的一项重大制度设计和创新，在服务</span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">&ldquo;三教&rdquo;改革、推动职业教育高质量发展方面发挥了重要作用。大赛涵盖了多个学科和领域，涉及多个层次和类型的职业院校，具有广泛的参与性和综合性</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">为职业院校</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">师生</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">提供了一个交流互鉴的平台，</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">为</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">进一步提升我省技术技能人才培养质量</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">，起到了</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">&ldquo;树旗、导航、定标、催化&rdquo;</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">的</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">作用</span></span><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;">。</span></span></p>');
INSERT INTO content
                    VALUES (240, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">5月24日，江西省职业教育学会艺术专业委员会(以下简称艺委会)重点工作部署会暨江西省职业教育学会艺术专业委员会红色文化创作基地揭牌仪式在江西软件大学井冈山校区召开。江西省职业教育学会艺委会主任单位和副主任单位、相关院校及企业单位的代表参加。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微���雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A36%3A28%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2063842589&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=REi9f8gYMIvmgRutdm5eywbJu9I%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A36%3A28%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2063842589&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=REi9f8gYMIvmgRutdm5eywbJu9I%3D" width="650" height="487" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">上午，艺委会相关人员参观江西软件大学井冈山校区《红色文化师生获奖作品展》，艺委会召开了副主任以上委员工作会。会议讨论并通过艺委会各工作部部长、副部长人选及各专业工作部的工作职责及主要工作计划。同时，会上讨论通过职业院校师生作品设计大赛方案及走访名校名企工作方案。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: center; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A37%3A06%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2063842627&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=dnaA7PO1IJG6yVHYdtJMQzQRsYA%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1);" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A37%3A06%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2063842627&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=dnaA7PO1IJG6yVHYdtJMQzQRsYA%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">下午进行了&ldquo;红色文化创作基地&rdquo;揭牌仪式及产品设计工作部成立大会。会上，井冈山市人民政府副市长刘济光对各位领导、专家的到来表示欢迎。他指出在这片红色沃土上搭建红色文化创作基地，就是要以职业教育的创新实践为笔，以艺术创作的独特语言为墨，在新时代续写红色文化传承的新篇章。希望以此次基地揭牌为起点，携手在这片充满希望的土地上，用画笔勾勒初心，用创意激活传统，用匠心培育人才，让井冈山精神在艺术的诠释中历久弥新，让职业教育在红色的浸润中根深叶茂！</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;" align="justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A38%3A00%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2063842680&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=EPoY%2BCI6u4dTlTr7pYw207r%2Fk78%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A38%3A00%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2063842680&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=EPoY%2BCI6u4dTlTr7pYw207r%2Fk78%3D" width="650" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">江西软件大学井冈山校区管委会副主任于涛介绍了学校建设情况和所获荣誉。自2022年4月承接首次写生业务以来累计完成1500余名学生写生活动，形成&ldquo;红色文化+艺术创作+数字技术&rdquo;的特色实践模式。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">江西软件大学VR与艺术学院副院长、江西省职业教育学会艺委会副主任帅茨平介绍了红色文化创作基地基本情况。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
