<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A41%3A50%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png?Expires=2063842910&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=dWmYHxiz2u3deAeM1YrhPSITlW0%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A41%3A50%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png?Expires=2063842910&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=dWmYHxiz2u3deAeM1YrhPSITlW0%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" /></a></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">该基地是由江西省职业教育学会艺术专业委员会与井冈山先锋红培基地（省教育厅&ldquo;大思政课&rdquo;实践教学基地）联合共建的实体平台，旨在以井冈山红色文化资源为依托，将红色革命精神与艺术创作、思政教育深度融合。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;">会后，艺委会主任刘彦宣布产品设计工作部成立并向工作部成员颁发聘书。江西软件大学当选为产品设计工作部部长单位，江西软件大学VR与艺术学院副院长、江西省职业教育学会艺委会副主任帅茨平担任该工作部部长。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; color: #333333; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A26%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png?Expires=2063842947&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=FoLJEZlVeRV0ezoD5%2B9VKjt8niI%3D" data-fancybox="gallery"><img class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; text-decoration-line: none; list-style-type: none; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A26%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png?Expires=2063842947&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=FoLJEZlVeRV0ezoD5%2B9VKjt8niI%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" /></a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; transition: 0.3s ease-in;" href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2025-05-29%2009%3A42%3A52%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png?Expires=2063842972&amp;